description:
We are a global IT company specializing in software development projects. We are willing to work on your project and deliver a high standard output within tight timescales.
Since you are looking for a full-time developer we can offer you collaboration within outstaffing model, in fact, it’s your external full-time employee (and even more if it's necessary to accomplish a task):
1.    we provide you with highly skilled professional developers (if needed we can replace or enlarge your developer team in shortest terms);
2.    we guarantee you full control over task progress, and you can freely contact with your developer(s) via Skype, Telegram, etc.;
3.    we can also assign our project manager to your team to control deadlines and task accomplishing quality or you can control it yourself.
Why you should work with us:
1.    we successfully accomplished over 150 projects since our foundation in 2009;
2.    there are more than 50 professional developers in our team, mostly of them have Master’s degrees in Computer Science or related areas;
3.    over 65% of our clients come back to us with new projects;
4.    we work in any format you are comfortable with: fixed price, time & material, outstaffing, etc.;
5.   we have very advantageous rates as our company is situated in the regional centre of Russia, all our developers work on-site.
Please, feel free to contact if you have any interest or questions, and, please, note that we can work with almost all technologies: we have Front-end developers, Back-end developers, Full stack developers, mobile app developers (iOS, Android and Windows Phone), etc. Our expertise is really wide and covers almost all technologies.
